go 1.26

// VORTEX Go workspace.
//
// The whole platform compiles into a single binary (Non-Negotiable Rule #1),
// so for now there is exactly one module rooted at the repository root. As the
// build plan progresses (e.g. the Go plugin SDK in M6.3), additional modules
// such as ./plugins/sdk-go may be added here with their own `use` directives.
use .
